mmac-24
Target Report Undocumented Warn(%qs is deprecated)

mtelephony
Target Report RejectNegative Warn(%qs is deprecated)
Enable Dual and Single Operand Instructions for Telephony.

mxy
Target Report
Enable XY Memory extension (DSP version 3).

