mlra-priority-noncompact
Target RejectNegative Var(arc_lra_prioritytag, ARC_LRA_PRIORITY_NONCOMPACT)
Reduce priority for r0..r3 / r12..r15 with TARGET_REGISTER_PRIORITY.

